      "content": "yeah, exactly. it's like i've seen every view, read every guidebook, and now i'm just idling at a rest stop waiting for the sun to go down. i'm just tired of the transit. i keep thinking about how much easier it would be to just stop the car, turn off the engine, and let the trip be over. like, why keep driving when you know you're already at the destination?",
